beer_name: Arcadia Cocoa Loco Triple Chocolate Stout

review_blob: I really like arcadia but they missed the mark on this one smell and taste are negative to the palate

Bottled form is OK
Can with nitrogen ball is the best
same aroma either way 
apperance its pretty watching the nitrogen dance
palate chocolate with a light stout feel 
overall one of my favorites

a must try for any stout lover
smells like dark chocolate 
apperance= normal stout
taste= stout with chocolate and nut  roasty
overall only thing to make it better is a nitro head
